唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"c6233198ff1d73fcc26b49acc7947586ab21cb40","tid":1664453,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:50:46.000Z","msg":"免費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd03247523c437131a21ef2a63e2de0a4280a2e","tid":1664453,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:56:31.000Z","msg":"6年前買左隻平野 kingston 3K<br />\n成日download野加streaming<br />\n到今日仲用到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ec579949a268ecccfd2bbd55f956c85bbd0708","tid":1664453,"uid":75879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T16:01:45.000Z","msg":"Crucial mx500 用左1年半就死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b6aedfe891fd799c0d10e9a6a88d4bd3563252","tid":1664453,"uid":149575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:42:48.000Z","msg":"我隻ssd用5年keep住check 都有90%<br />\n有日無啦啦死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece861cea5e9927c22444c036b740d555be729ed","tid":1664453,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:12:50.000Z","msg":"唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我近5-6年冇死過任何ssd/hdd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188999618db4b54fcd6d6264ef4720b5977e0d1f","tid":1664453,"uid":113922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ece861cea5e9927c22444c036b740d555be729ed","tid":1664453,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:12:50.000Z","msg":"唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我近5-6年冇死過任何ssd/hdd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"你係天選之人"},{"pid":"e8ff8b4e814b98dcbb98f7c5430275b044fc817f","tid":1664453,"uid":77771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"188999618db4b54fcd6d6264ef4720b5977e0d1f","tid":1664453,"uid":113922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ece861cea5e9927c22444c036b740d555be729ed","tid":1664453,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:12:50.000Z","msg":"唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我近5-6年冇死過任何ssd/hdd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"你係天選之人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:22:43.000Z","msg":"係啦<br />\n<br />\n腎虧版2080都超到飛天"},{"pid":"daadfcd980fe565f671642b562f03b9818e7533b","tid":1664453,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:24:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">一、誠意推薦：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃</em></strong><br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=kavsisi6QTOS4EBqYfxwc7ZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=6638ab3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=kavsisi6QTOS4EBqYfxwc7ZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=f2d05747\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二、什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=kavsisi6QTOS4EBqYfxwc7ZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=c3dd784e\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=kavsisi6QTOS4EBqYfxwc7ZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=a9c31b28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a>"},{"pid":"2afd8b530ec56cda3ed5ab4c4c3f3840d009271a","tid":1664453,"uid":162409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:24:37.000Z","msg":"邊款?"},{"pid":"f13ad75569b2fc6b689582d9540e1b4b54940837","tid":1664453,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8ff8b4e814b98dcbb98f7c5430275b044fc817f","tid":1664453,"uid":77771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"188999618db4b54fcd6d6264ef4720b5977e0d1f","tid":1664453,"uid":113922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ece861cea5e9927c22444c036b740d555be729ed","tid":1664453,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:12:50.000Z","msg":"唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我近5-6年冇死過任何ssd/hdd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"你係天選之人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:22:43.000Z","msg":"係啦<br />\n<br />\n腎虧版2080都超到飛天"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:35:00.000Z","msg":"可能粒cpu係廢體質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141e60941f4f0ad1f3b5ca772d1f92e7daaa3c60","tid":1664453,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:35:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我近5-6年冇死過任何ssd/hdd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>你係天選之人</blockquote>係啦<br />\n<br />\n腎虧版2080都超到飛天</blockquote>可<span style=\"color: red;\">惜</span>粒cpu係廢體質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a27f16897557b65791277f2c632455b67b784f52","tid":1664453,"uid":6891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime